---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="FAQs | BodyByAls"
  description="Transform your fitness journey with BodyByAls Online Coaching. Get easy-to-follow workouts, sustainable nutrition guidance, and hormone-based strategies from Coach Anton Soler. Train anywhere, eat smarter, and build lasting healthy habits.">
  <!-- Page Header Section Start -->
  <div class="page-header bg-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <!-- Page Header Box Start -->
          <div class="page-header-box">
            <h1 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            <nav class="wow fadeInUp">
              <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">home</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">FAQS</li>
              </ol>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <!-- Page Header Box End -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Page Header Section End -->

  <!-- Page Faqs Start -->
  <div class="page-faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <!-- Page Single Sidebar Start -->
          <div class="page-single-sidebar">
            <!-- Page Category List Start -->
            <div class="page-category-list wow fadeInUp">
              <ul>
                <li><a href="#faq_1">General Questions</a></li>
                <li><a href="#faq_2">Program & Coaching</a></li>
                <li><a href="#faq_3">Nutrition & Meal Plans</a></li>
                <li><a href="#faq_4">Payment & Getting Started</a></li>
                <li><a href="#faq_5">Results & Support</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Page Category List End -->
          </div>
          <!-- Page Single Sidebar End -->
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <!-- Page FAQs Category Start -->
          <div class="page-faqs-catagery">
            <!-- FAQs Section 1: General Questions -->
            <div class="page-single-faqs" id="faq_1">
              <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">General Questions</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-accordion our-faq-accordion" id="accordion">
                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading1">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse1"
                      aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse1">
                      Q1. Is BODYBYALS suitable for beginners?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse1"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="heading1"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Yes. BODYBYALS is beginner-friendly. Our workouts are easy to follow, with proper form guidance
                        and progressions based on your level, lifestyle, and goals.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading2">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse2"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse2">
                      Q2. Can I do BODYBYALS even if I'm busy or working full-time?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse2"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading2"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Absolutely. Our program is designed for busy individuals. You can train at home or anywhere, at
                        your own time and pace. We have clients all over the world including the Philippines, USA,
                        Dubai, Singapore, Australia, and many more — so the program works across different schedules and
                        time zones.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading3">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse3"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse3">
                      Q3. Is this program suitable for PCOS, insulin resistance, or postpartum clients?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse3"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading3"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Yes. BODYBYALS focuses on controlling hormones and improving insulin sensitivity through proper
                        training and nutrition.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQs Section 1 End -->

            <!-- FAQs Section 2: Program & Coaching -->
            <div class="page-single-faqs" id="faq_2">
              <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">Program & Coaching</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-accordion our-faq-accordion" id="accordion1">
                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading4">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse4"
                      aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse4">
                      Q1. Do I need gym equipment?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse4"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="heading4"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion1">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        For beginners, we don't recommend lifting weights right away to prevent injuries. We start with
                        bodyweight exercises to build proper form and foundation. For clients who already know how to
                        work out, we can include weights based on your capacity and experience.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading5">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse5"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse5">
                      Q2. What's included in the BODYBYALS Online Coaching and Nutrition Guide?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse5"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading5"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion1">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>You'll get:</p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>A free consultation call before you join to answer all your questions</li>
                        <li>Easy-to-follow workout programs tailored to your lifestyle</li>
                        <li>Coach Anton's Nutrition Guide, discussed in a separate call</li>
                        <li>Chat support where you can send meal photos and progress updates</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading6">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse6"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse6">
                      Q3. What makes BODYBYALS different from other programs?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse6"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading6"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion1">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>We focus on:</p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Controlling hormones, not calorie counting</li>
                        <li>A sustainable nutrition guide, not extreme dieting</li>
                        <li>Real food and healthy carb alternatives</li>
                        <li>Long-term results by building healthy habits</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading7">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse7"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse7">
                      Q4. Are BODYBYALS products required to join the program?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse7"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading7"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion1">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        No, they are optional. However, BODYBYALS Shirataki Rice and Keto Bread are great healthy carb
                        alternatives to help you stay consistent while enjoying your meals.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQs Section 2 End -->

            <!-- FAQs Section 3: Nutrition & Meal Plans -->
            <div class="page-single-faqs" id="faq_3">
              <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">Nutrition & Meal Plans</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-accordion our-faq-accordion" id="accordion2">
                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading8">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse8"
                      aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse8">
                      Q1. What is the BODYBYALS Nutrition Guide? Is it keto?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse8"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="heading8"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion2">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        The BODYBYALS Nutrition Guide is an Insulin Sensitivity Reset Diet. We don't count calories.
                        Instead, we focus on controlling hormones. This guide is suitable whether you have PCOS, want to
                        lose weight, have hormonal imbalance, are trying to get pregnant, are postpartum, or simply want
                        to be healthier overall.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        The guide teaches you what to eat, when to eat, what to avoid, and how to enjoy your favorite
                        foods without guilt.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading9">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse9"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse9">
                      Q2. What's included in the BODYBYALS Meal Plan?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse9"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading9"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion2">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        The meal plan is low-carb and high-protein, also called the Insulin Sensitivity Reset Diet. It's
                        seed oil–free, chef-prepared and filling, and designed to support insulin sensitivity and
                        hormone balance. Premium packages include USDA Prime Ribeye Steak and Salmon.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading10">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse10"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse10">
                      Q3. How many meals per day are included in the meal plan?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse10"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading10"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion2">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>We offer different options based on eating capacity:</p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Premium and Superior Packages:</strong> 2 meals per day, intentionally designed to support
                          hormone balance and better insulin response. These are suitable for heavy eaters.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Lite Package:</strong> 2 bowls per day — 1 bowl for lunch and 1 bowl for dinner — suitable
                          for light eaters.
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading11">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse11"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse11">
                      Q4. Can I customize my meal plan?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse11"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading11"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion2">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Menu options vary by package. Our team will guide you in choosing the best option based on your
                        goals and lifestyle.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQs Section 3 End -->

            <!-- FAQs Section 4: Payment & Getting Started -->
            <div class="page-single-faqs" id="faq_4">
              <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">Payment & Getting Started</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-accordion our-faq-accordion" id="accordion3">
                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading12">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse12"
                      aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse12">
                      Q1. Is installment payment available?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse12"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="heading12"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion3">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        <strong>For the BODYBYALS Meal Plan:</strong> Yes! Installment options are available and can be discussed
                        during a call so we can explain the terms clearly and guide you properly.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        <strong>For BODYBYALS Online Coaching & Nutrition Guide:</strong> Packages are paid in full. After
                        proof of transaction, we will schedule another call to walk you through the Nutrition Guide.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading13">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse13"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse13">
                      Q2. How do I start?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse13"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading13"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion3">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        You can book a free consultation call so we can explain the program and help you choose what's
                        best for you.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQs Section 4 End -->

            <!-- FAQs Section 5: Results & Support -->
            <div class="page-single-faqs" id="faq_5">
              <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">Results & Support</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-accordion our-faq-accordion" id="accordion4">
                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading14">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse14"
                      aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse14">
                      Q1. How does chat support work?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse14"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="heading14"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion4">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Clients can send meal photos, questions, and progress updates through chat. Our team provides
                        guidance and feedback to help you stay consistent and on track.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->

                <!-- FAQ Item Start -->
                <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading15">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#collapse15"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controls="collapse15">
                      Q2. When will I start seeing results?
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="collapse15"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="heading15"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordion4">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>
                        Results depend on consistency. For BODYBYALS Online Coaching & Nutrition Guide, long-lasting
                        results come from following the workouts and nutrition guide properly. The same applies to the
                        Meal Plan — consistent adherence leads to better and sustainable results.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item End -->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- FAQs Section 5 End -->
          </div>
          <!-- Page FAQs Category End -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Page Faqs End -->
</Layout>
